Slightly modified roomNode sketchbook

The PIR_PORT has been disabled.



---- OUTPUT --------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Serial output

The serial output takes place via 57600 baud if not defined otherwise
  (can be defined via #define SERIAL_BAUD 57600)

The serial output looks like the following:
ROOM 103 0 59 235 0

ROOM 102 0 59 235 0
ROOM 215 0 59 235 0
ROOM 235 0 59 235 0
ROOM 113 0 59 235 0
ROOM 90 0 59 235 0

ROOM is defined and cannot be changed. The other values are defined in the
order as the following struct

struct {
    byte light;     // light sensor: 0..255
    byte moved :1;  // motion detector: 0..1
    byte humi  :7;  // humidity: 0..100
    int temp   :10; // temperature: -500..+500 (tenths)
    byte lobat :1;  // supply voltage dropped under 3.1V: 0..1
} payload;


